Interface DeclarationsVisitor<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
DeclarationsBaseVisitor
public interface DeclarationsVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by DeclarationsParser.
